  "id": "sinxs-sea-ice-thickness",
  "stac_version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The dataset comprises monthly averaged sea-ice and, to a lesser extent, snow thickness fields on a common grid (EASE2 and with a common grid spacing (12.5 or 25 km). Data stem from models, reanalyses, satellite observations (radar/lidar altimetry, passive microwave and thermal infrared), airborne and ULS measurements. A consistent set of netCDF metadata facilitates comparison. The dataset has been produced within the ESA-funded SIN'XS project",
